caption.text:
How to DOUBLE your story views 👇

I put together a few KEY RULES our clients follow to double their story views. 

Here they are:

1️⃣ Take a break from posting stories every week. A break = don’t post stories for 24 hours.

2️⃣ Every 5 stories, add either a poll or a quiz. The more people click, hold, answer = engage, the more story views.

3️⃣ Every 3 stories, post a new type of story: text, talking head, screenshot, etc. Don’t post 5 stories in a row of you talking.

4️⃣ Show your face (ideally, your very first story can be a selfie).

5️⃣ Don’t use automated captions (people don’t read them as it’s more time-consuming than just pausing, reading, and keeping scrolling).

6️⃣ Don’t overload stories with text (no more than 5-6 lines of text per story).

7️⃣ Don’t post video stories that are longer than 15 seconds. Keep them shorter (5-10 seconds).

Implement a few of these hacks today, and your story views will go up.

Comment the word ENGAGEMENT and I’ll dm you my new PDF with TOP-18 hacks to double your engagement on Instagram
